655
00:48:30,280 --> 00:48:31,240
Please take me in.

656
00:48:31,320 --> 00:48:33,200
-Hey!
-[man 6] I can do everything.

657
00:48:33,280 --> 00:48:36,160
He has bought so many.
He won't buy any more of you.

658
00:48:36,480 --> 00:48:39,000
-Why don't you understand?
-[man 7] But I'm a hard worker.

659
00:48:39,280 --> 00:48:42,600
[Prik] Hey. Go back home for today.

660
00:48:42,680 --> 00:48:44,880
You can come back some other day.
He is not buying any more.

661
00:48:44,960 --> 00:48:46,520
-Leave. Just go!
-[man 7] Please take me in.

662
00:48:46,600 --> 00:48:48,720
-[Prik] Leave!
-Lady Karaked.

663
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:51,240
-[woman 2] Please take me in.
