664
00:48:51,520 --> 00:48:52,360
I'm--

665
00:48:52,640 --> 00:48:54,840
-[Prik] Go!
-[man 6] Lady Karaked.

666
00:48:55,360 --> 00:48:57,240
[woman 2] Please take me in.

667
00:48:57,320 --> 00:48:58,640
-[man 6] Lady Karaked.
-[Prik] Go!

668
00:48:58,760 --> 00:48:59,760
-Leave.
-Lady Karaked.

669
00:48:59,840 --> 00:49:01,920
-I'm here.
-[Champa] Karaked.

670
00:49:02,160 --> 00:49:04,440
-[man 6] Please take me in. I work hard.
-[woman 1] Lady Karaked.

671
00:49:04,520 --> 00:49:05,440
[Prik] Go!

672
00:49:07,640 --> 00:49:09,640
-[woman 1] Please take me in.
-[man 6] Please take me in.

673
00:49:10,120 --> 00:49:11,040
Prik.

674
00:49:11,120 --> 00:49:12,360
[woman 3] I work hard.

675
00:49:12,440 --> 00:49:14,760
-[man 6] Lady Karaked.
-[woman 2] Please take me in.

676
00:49:15,080 --> 00:49:15,920
Yes?

677
00:49:16,400 --> 00:49:17,480
Why are they here?

678
00:49:17,800 --> 00:49:20,120
[chuckles]
They are selling themselves as slaves.

679
00:49:20,960 --> 00:49:21,920
Oh!

680
00:49:22,560 --> 00:49:25,480
[Champa] I have bought ten of them already
in the last couple of days.

681
00:49:26,040 --> 00:49:27,160
I won't buy any more.

682
00:49:27,240 --> 00:49:29,000
[man 7] Please take me in. I work hard.

683
00:49:29,080 --> 00:49:30,200
[man 6] Lady Karaked.

684
00:49:30,280 --> 00:49:31,840
-All of you.
-[woman 3] Please take me in.

685
00:49:32,200 --> 00:49:34,600
Why do you want
to sell yourselves here so much?

686
00:49:35,560 --> 00:49:39,040
[all] I want a net. I want a net.

687
00:49:39,320 --> 00:49:41,280
-I want a net.
-[man 6] Please take me in.

688
00:49:41,680 --> 00:49:43,720
-Please take me in.
-[man 7] Me too.

689
00:49:43,800 --> 00:49:45,440
-[woman 3] I want a net.
-[man 6] Lady Karaked.

690
00:49:45,520 --> 00:49:47,000
-Please help me.
-[woman 2] I want a net.

691
00:49:47,080 --> 00:49:48,960
-[man 6] I work hard. I'm strong.
-[woman 2] My lady.

692
00:49:49,040 --> 00:49:50,200
I want a net.

693
00:49:50,280 --> 00:49:52,520
-[man 7] I want a net.
-[woman 3] I work hard. I want a net.

694
00:49:52,600 --> 00:49:53,760
[man 6] I can do everything.

695
00:49:53,840 --> 00:49:55,120
[all] Take me in.

696
00:50:02,440 --> 00:50:04,080
It's because of the nets.

697
00:50:05,360 --> 00:50:06,640
This is surprising.

698
00:50:07,760 --> 00:50:08,760
[scoffs]

699
00:50:09,160 --> 00:50:11,520
Do you realize what you have done?

700
00:50:12,880 --> 00:50:14,160
What do you mean, Lady Champa?

701
00:50:15,160 --> 00:50:16,040
[scoffs]

702
00:50:17,440 --> 00:50:18,640
Are they all gone, Prik?

703
00:50:19,120 --> 00:50:20,040
Yes, my lady.

704
00:50:20,360 --> 00:50:24,360
I'll wait at the pier to chase them away.

705
00:50:24,920 --> 00:50:26,040
Chase who away?

706
00:50:26,520 --> 00:50:28,400
The people

707
00:50:29,120 --> 00:50:31,560
who want to sell themselves
as slaves here.

708
00:50:31,920 --> 00:50:33,920
There will be many more.

709
00:50:34,640 --> 00:50:37,560
