710
00:50:39,480 --> 00:50:41,040
They are saying that

711
00:50:41,760 --> 00:50:44,400
at Marquess Horathibodi's house,

712
00:50:44,480 --> 00:50:49,160
there are mosquito nets
given to every servant for free.

713
00:50:50,760 --> 00:50:51,600
[scoffs]

714
00:50:51,680 --> 00:50:52,960
What are you going to do now?

715
00:50:54,720 --> 00:50:56,520
If you buy more servants,

716
00:50:56,800 --> 00:50:58,520
I'll buy more nets.

717
00:50:59,560 --> 00:51:02,360
Now I know you are so wealthy.

718
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:04,160
You have so much money to spend.

719
00:51:04,720 --> 00:51:06,400
[sighs]
Chuang, let's go.

720
00:51:06,880 --> 00:51:07,720
Yes, my lady.

721
00:51:08,960 --> 00:51:09,960
[scoffs]

722
00:51:15,320 --> 00:51:16,800
I think they are commoners

723
00:51:17,680 --> 00:51:19,960
who don't want to be conscript soldiers.

724
00:51:20,040 --> 00:51:21,480
I think so too.

725
00:51:22,560 --> 00:51:24,560
Or they want to avoid paying taxes.

726
00:51:25,840 --> 00:51:27,800
[Horathibodi] There are many of them
that are lazy.

727
00:51:29,080 --> 00:51:31,080
They don't want to work for the crown
or pay taxes.

728
00:51:32,120 --> 00:51:34,760
Being slaves in masters' houses is easier.

729
00:51:36,240 --> 00:51:38,120
Being slaves is easier?

730
00:51:41,640 --> 00:51:42,840
It is so.

731
00:51:44,160 --> 00:51:46,840
To ensure they can fill their stomachs
and not go hungry.

732
00:51:48,240 --> 00:51:49,800
I see.

733
00:51:53,560 --> 00:51:54,560
Karaked.

734
00:51:56,640 --> 00:51:57,920
I still don't understand

735
00:51:58,560 --> 00:52:00,280
the thing about Count Surasakorn.

736
00:52:01,960 --> 00:52:05,840
Do you have anything else
to tell my father?

737
00:52:07,800 --> 00:52:09,080
You know exactly what I'm thinking.

738
00:52:10,680 --> 00:52:12,560
