739
00:52:13,960 --> 00:52:15,040
[sighs]

740
00:52:16,160 --> 00:52:17,240
No.

741
00:52:18,640 --> 00:52:19,560
But...

742
00:52:19,920 --> 00:52:24,200
Are you worried that he might be harmful
to Duke Kosathibodi?

743
00:52:26,000 --> 00:52:28,440
Do you really think so, Karaked?

744
00:52:28,960 --> 00:52:32,680
He might be or might not be.

745
00:52:36,120 --> 00:52:37,680
How do you know about him?

746
00:52:38,600 --> 00:52:42,160
He's both a good man and a bad man.

747
00:52:42,520 --> 00:52:43,760
[Karaked] So, I can't tell.

748
00:52:44,560 --> 00:52:45,760
But Lord Hora

749
00:52:47,160 --> 00:52:48,120
and <i><font color="white">Khun Pi,</font></i>

750
00:52:49,680 --> 00:52:52,240
shouldn't we be cautious?

751
00:52:54,200 --> 00:52:55,280
How?

752
00:52:56,040 --> 00:52:57,760
We should assume he's a bad man.

753
00:52:59,480 --> 00:53:03,080
I won't sell anything to
the British East India Company this time.

754
00:53:04,560 --> 00:53:06,240
Those two westerners are deceitful.

755
00:53:07,360 --> 00:53:09,040
They even committed fraud
against their company.

756
00:53:15,960 --> 00:53:16,920
You should leave.

757
00:53:17,840 --> 00:53:19,840
[foreboding music]

758
00:53:27,040 --> 00:53:29,040
[foreboding music continues]

