from the same breasts.

768
00:54:27,440 --> 00:54:29,080
He's also one of his close friends

769
00:54:29,560 --> 00:54:32,080
and they fought in wars together.

770
00:54:32,640 --> 00:54:36,000
Now he serves as the head of Treasury.

771
00:54:37,480 --> 00:54:38,760
He makes a lot of profit for it.

